詩人、劇作家和導演，主要從事泰盧固語電影工作。他曾參與過 750 多部電影，包括泰米爾語、卡納達語和印地語。他曾三次獲得安得拉邦南迪獎。","name":"塔尼克拉·巴拉尼","primary":false}}]}},"person_2091760_translations":{"at":1774727010559,"data":{"id":2091760,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Wu Jin Yan, born in Chengdu, China, began studying ballet at the age of 3. In 2000, she moved to Beijing to train at the Dance School Affiliated with the Beijing Dance Academy, aiming to become a professional ballerina. After seven years of training, she joined the National Ballet of China but suffered recurring foot fractures, which led her to shift career paths. In 2009, she enrolled at the Beijing Film Academy to study acting.\n\nOn September 13, 2024, it was announced that Wu Jin Yan married fellow actor Hong Yao.","name":"Wu Jinyan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吴谨言，1990年8月16日出生于四川省都江堰，毕业于北京电影学院，中国内地影视女演员。\n\n2013年，凭借在民国剧《烽火佳人》中饰演性格迥异的孪生姐妹而崭露头角。2015年，因在清宫历史剧《多情江山》中婉儿一角受到关注 [3]  ，同年，她还主演抗战剧《激战》。2018年，凭借宫斗剧《延禧攻略》获第24届华鼎奖中国古代题材电视剧最佳女演员奖；同年，主演青春喜剧片《说走就走之不说再见》。2019年，主演的古装剧《皓镧传》播出。","name":"吴谨言","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"吳謹言","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"오근언","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Ngô Cẩn Ngôn là một nữ diễn viên người Trung Quốc, nổi tiếng nhờ vai diễn Lệnh Ý Hoàng quý phi Ngụy Anh Lạc trong bộ phim Diên Hi Công Lược.","name":"Ngô Cẩn Ngôn","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"吳謹言，1990 年 8 月 16 日出生於四川省都江堰，畢業於北京電影學院，中國內地影視女演員。\n\n2013 年，憑藉在民國劇《烽火佳人》中飾演性格迥異的孿生姐妹而嶄露頭角。2015 年，因在清宮歷史劇《多情江山》中婉兒一角受到關注 ，同年，她還主演抗戰劇《激戰》。2018 年，憑藉宮鬥劇《延禧攻略》獲第 24 屆華鼎獎中國古代題材電視劇最佳女演員獎；同年，主演青春喜劇片《説走就走之不説再見》。2019 年，主演的古裝劇《皓鑭傳》播出。","name":"吳謹言","primary":false}}]}},"movie_526034_credits":{"at":1774727020103,"data":{"id":526034,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1786561,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Jenna Laurenzo","original_name":"Jenna Laurenzo","popularity":0.3812,"profile_path":"/7QQkzwcmEvvYrsPR58aJZhtEmSm.jpg","cast_id":12,"character":"Lauren Anderson","credit_id":"5bbfc6d10e0a266e59008c4d","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":227989,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Caitlin Mehner","original_name":"Caitlin Mehner","popularity":0.74,"profile_path":"/yohvb88GuHBAphAxNIcYgsDy3BK.jpg","cast_id":7,"character":"Hailey","credit_id":"5bbfc412c3a3682d60009610","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1817198,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Brandon Micheal Hall","original_name":"Brandon Micheal Hall","popularity":0.3668,"profile_path":"/ocdCkFUC5HxewOiPo4wiXmHt6Wo.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Austin","credit_id":"5bbfc3c00e0a266e5b008da3","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":26472,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Steve Guttenberg","original_name":"Steve Guttenberg","popularity":2.2604,"profile_path":"/ghTMepliFNcRQHNELs8pgNDsZyW.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"Mike","credit_id":"5bbfc3c80e0a266e5b008dbb","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":55422,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Elaine Hendrix","original_name":"Elaine Hendrix","popularity":2.006,"profile_path":"/ajnxlCCO0IYQeaL2KOJwjFWkFG0.jpg","cast_id":5,"character":"Maggie","credit_id":"5bbfc3fcc3a3682d440096f3","order":4},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":77013,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Deirdre O'Connell","original_name":"Deirdre O'Connell","popularity":1.799,"profile_path":"/14e0AZOZafenduP7O6oMLSL92RP.jpg","cast_id":9,"character":"Rose Anderson","credit_id":"5bbfc42392514179c1008